org.swisscheese.swisscheese.engine.rendering

Class StripRendererDispatcher

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.swisscheese.swisscheese.engine.rendering.Renderer
      • org.swisscheese.swisscheese.engine.rendering.MultithreadedRendererDispatcher
        • org.swisscheese.swisscheese.engine.rendering.StripRendererDispatcher

  • public class StripRendererDispatcher
extends MultithreadedRendererDispatcher
    A class for dispatching the threads to work on RenderStrip class. The "Strip-Rendering" strategy involves assigning each vertical scan of the screen "Strip" to a new thread to render. However, the performance of the StripRendererDispatcher is equal to or worse than SingleThreadedRenderer, likely as a result of object creation.
    (n times more objects and primitives created, where n is the width of the screen).
    Since:
    2019-01-06, v0.5
    Version:
    v1.0
    Author:
    Alex Kalinins
